quote><br />\n大英祖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e56d470d3c7320045435346afe1f555a7df115f","tid":490744,"uid":37935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T12:18:31.000Z","msg":"沙中線 57億/km vs 中九龍幹線 90億/km<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170626/s00002/1498412824237\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170626%2Fs00002%2F1498412824237&d=Dj16aHTGWLAWY3FyFSablp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=5cb72147\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170626%2Fs00002%2F1498412824237&h=5f24aa5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170626/s00002/1498412824237</a>"},{"pid":"93054ada922607e30c87968787588e62f0912b5e","tid":490744,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T12:21:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沙中線 57億/km vs 中九龍幹線 90億/km<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170626/s00002/1498412824237\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170626%2Fs00002%2F1498412824237&d=Dj16aHTGWLAWY3FyFSablp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=5cb72147\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170626%2Fs00002%2F1498412824237&h=5f24aa5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170626/s00002/1498412824237</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n痴撚線"},{"pid":"193cef5de0f3d392f8a8cb4997b7e116129d2d58","tid":490744,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T14:06:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁易超支其實主要原因係咪顧問太廢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為未做曬所有設計 探地就出標梗係爆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正解。<br />\n咁多隧道重要舊區地底</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一開始做哂盆數出黎，咁大，好難過頭一關，都係報細50%先，橫掂又無人知既，開火煮飯先，d錢係大家既，怕咩"},{"pid":"55679f048860bd9a6a84d2d9fbd0997d304c01bc","tid":490744,"uid":25689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T14:28:45.000Z","msg":"最後幾多錢都唔緊要<br />\n香港人一樣會硬食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f3075cb2e76865f36edd0015309eb5131582312","tid":490744,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T14:40:13.000Z","msg":"如果要平 好簡單 輸入外勞（限期合約／臨時性質）<br />\n不過你地又會反對"},{"pid":"14390db29efa4de98b4e8d622a326dc38833aea6","tid":490744,"uid":18167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T14:40:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁易超支其實主要原因係咪顧問太廢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為未做曬所有設計 探地就出標梗係爆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正解。<br />\n咁多隧道重要舊區地底</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一開始做哂盆數出黎，咁大，好難過頭一關，都係報細50%先，橫掂又無人知既，開火煮飯先，d錢係大家既，怕咩</blockquote><br />\n如果完成晒個設計至出標，判頭出價自然要完到工又夠低至做到<br />\n一定好過設計未完全就出左標先，再比人慢慢claim<br />\n<br />\n而家設計係有幾簡單畫到咁簡單，實際情況有差別就好易比人claim VO<br />\n而且難度加大左，時間就要耐左，又可以俾人claim延期<br />\n<br />\n有VO要加野，又俾人禁住搶，明明唔貴搞到掂，但個個叫高幾倍試下執<br />\n<br />\n仲要近年樓市又旺, 基建又多, 澳門又吸左大堆工人過去，工人人工直線人升<br />\n<br />\n03,04年果時緊係平，個個都冇工開，個個鬥開賤價，唔係就唔洗開工<br />\n但當時港府就收起晒所有基建，07,08年樓市升溫就順勢搞埋十大基建<br />\n唔天價工程就奇"},{"pid":"a17b04afa4f6f044b5cfc0ef20086dd77211d31e","tid":490744,"uid":18167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T14:45:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果要平 好簡單 輸入外勞（限期合約／臨時性質）<br />\n不過你地又會反對</blockquote><br />\n但輸入外勞個情況好惡性<br />\n輸入之後工人人工下降，本地人就唔會再願意做工人<br />\n本地工人數減少，進一步靠外勞頂住個行業"},{"pid":"26172375664a6c9c3501827c1e9d64e5d7d4e29c","tid":490744,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T14:49:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果要平 好簡單 輸入外勞（限期合約／臨時性質）<br />\n不過你地又會反對</blockquote><br />\n但輸入外勞個情況好惡性<br />\n輸入之後工人人工下降，本地人就唔會再願意做工人<br />\n本地工人數減少，進一步靠外勞頂住個行業</blockquote><br />\n其實依賴外勞本質上無問題<br />\n不過大陸輸入太多低端人口來香港 政府被迫顧及佢地保護佢地飯碗<br />\n京津穗深滬等等一線城市基本上無本地工人 全部係外（省）勞"}]}